Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.35,0:20:05.90,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(961,65.714)}{\c&HCF87DF&}我的内心受到触动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.27,0:20:09.65,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(961,65.714)}{\c&HCF87DF&}我想守护你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:13.53,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(961,65.714)}{\c&HCF87DF&}这份心意是如此真诚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.03,0:20:17.12,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(961,65.714)}{\c&HCF87DF&}就算觉得没有结果还是说出了口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:21.04,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(961,65.714)}{\c&HCF87DF&}这样心里或许能轻松一点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.33,0:20:24.75,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(961,65.714)}{\c&HCF87DF&}迈出了这一步之后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.75,0:20:28.54,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(961,65.714)}{\c&HCF87DF&}梦想能否化为现实
